overview: "SKE48 Tandoku Concert 10-Shuunen Totsunyuu Haru no Fan Matsuri! ~Tomodachi 100-nin Dekiru ka na?" is a concert that was held by SKE48 in Nippon Gaishi Hall on April 28, 2018.  "SKE48 Tandoku Concert ~Sakae Fan Nyuugakushiki~" is a concert that was held by SKE48 in Saitama Super Arena on March 31, 2018.
tagline: ~SKE48 fan welcoming ceremony~ / 10th anniversary Spring Fan Special! ~Can we make 100 new friends?~
title: SKE48 Spring Concert 2018
